"Begin5008":
"So I hear there is a cake seller past the swarm of enemies here!
Very well! Let us get past this! "

"Allllright! It's done!
So, the cake seller should be right in front of us!
Nobody is going to stop us on our path! "

"Urrgh….it's disappointing about the cake, but I can't push my juniors too hard!
Sorry, I'm retreating! "

"I've been too engrossed in the cake……I've still got a long way to go.
So be it, I'm going to pretend I've fallen! "

"Hahahaha, my dear junior!
Don't push yourself too hard, rest a little!
We'll take care of the rest! "
